Interface PAULAFileConnector

All Known Implementing Classes:
PAULAConnector
public interface PAULAFileConnector

This interface describes only methods for Communication between a PAULAConnector and a Reader for the PAULA-structure. It describes a call back for parsing specific PAULA-Files.
